tags.description: A regional park close to downtown Kirkland in the Market neighborhood, featuring the historic Heritage Hall & gardens, tennis courts, a play area, interpretive walk, & a large grass field.

tags.description: Downtown and close to many restaurants and shops, Marina Park features a sandy beach, boat launch, public art, a beautiful open-air pavilion & magnificent views of Lake Washington and Seattle. Marina Park is home to many of Kirkland's special events.
tags.name: Marina Park
